  { '@type': 'Question', name: 'How long do testosterone gummies take to work?', acceptedAnswer: { '@type': 'Answer', text: 'The timeline varies by ingredient. Ashwagandha: cortisol reduction within 2 weeks, testosterone improvements at 8 to 12 weeks. Tongkat ali: cortisol reduction at 2 weeks, testosterone optimization at 4 to 6 weeks. Fenugreek: free testosterone improvements within 8 to 12 weeks. Zinc and vitamin D: 3 to 6 months to fully restore levels if deficient. D-aspartic acid: temporary testosterone increase within 12 days, though sustained effects are debated. For meaningful, measurable hormonal changes, plan on a minimum 8 to 12 week supplementation period with consistent daily dosing and supporting lifestyle factors.' } },
