    </div>

    <p>Natural testosterone gummies work through fundamentally different mechanisms than prescription testosterone replacement therapy (TRT). Rather than introducing exogenous testosterone, they support the body's own production by reducing cortisol (which directly suppresses testosterone synthesis), lowering sex hormone-binding globulin (SHBG) to free bound testosterone, providing essential cofactors for testosterone synthesis (zinc, vitamin D), and supporting Leydig cell function in the testes. This approach is safer and more appropriate for men with suboptimal but not clinically deficient testosterone levels.</p>

